In the present invention, the 1,3-dimethoxy-1,3-dihydroisobenzofuran-5-carboxylic acid succinimidyl ester is prepared according to the following process:
1) brominating 3,4-dimethylbenzoic acid, to prepare 3,4-bis(dibromomethyl)benzoic acid;
2) hydrolyzing 3,4-bis(dibromomethyl)benzoic acid, to obtain 3,4-diformylbenzoic acid;
